---
import TemplateLayout from "@/templates/movers-premium/TemplateLayout.astro";
---

<TemplateLayout
  title="Industries Served | RapidRelo Moving & Storage"
  description="Specialized relocation for offices, retail, and tech — RapidRelo's commercial moving expertise."
  active="industries"
  canonicalPath="/templates/movers-premium/industries"
>
<main>
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative bg-on-surface text-surface py-24 overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20">

</div>
<div class="relative max-w-rr-container-max mx-auto px-rr-margin-desktop z-10">
<div class="max-w-3xl">
<span class="inline-block bg-primary-container text-on-primary-fixed font-label-bold text-label-bold px-3 py-1 mb-stack-md uppercase tracking-widest">Sector Expertise</span>
<h1 class="font-rr-display-lg text-rr-display-lg-mobile md:text-rr-display-lg mb-rr-stack-lg leading-tight">
                        Specialized Moving for Every Sector.
                    </h1>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-surface-variant max-w-xl">
                        Logistics is more than moving boxes. It's about maintaining operational continuity. RapidRelo provides high-velocity relocation services tailored to your industry's specific compliance and hardware needs.
                    </p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Industry Grid: Bento Style -->
<section class="py-rr-stack-lg bg-surface">
<div class="max-w-rr-container-max mx-auto px-rr-margin-desktop">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
<!-- Corporate Offices -->
<div class="md:col-span-2 border-2 border-on-surface p-8 bg-surface-container-lowest flex flex-col justify-between block-shadow-hover transition-all">
<div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-stack-md">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" style="font-size: 40px;">corporate_fare</span>
<h3 class="font-rr-headline-sm text-rr-headline-sm uppercase">Corporate Offices</h3>
</div>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-rr-stack-lg">Scalable solutions for headquarters, regional branches, and rapidly growing teams. We manage the assets so you can manage the business.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-primary-container h-1 w-full"></div>
</div>
<!-- Retail & Boutiques -->
<div class="md:col-span-1 border-2 border-on-surface p-8 bg-surface-container-lowest flex flex-col justify-between block-shadow-hover transition-all">
<div>
<div class="mb-stack-md">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" style="font-size: 40px;">storefront</span>
<h3 class="font-rr-headline-sm text-rr-headline-sm uppercase mt-4">Retail &amp; Boutiques</h3>
</div>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Sensitive inventory handling and storefront setup for modern retailers.</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Tech & Data Centers -->
<div class="md:col-span-1 border-2 border-on-surface p-8 bg-on-surface text-surface flex flex-col justify-between block-shadow-hover transition-all">
<div>
<div class="mb-stack-md">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed" style="font-size: 40px;">dns</span>
<h3 class="font-rr-headline-sm text-rr-headline-sm uppercase mt-4">Tech &amp; Data Centers</h3>
</div>
<p class="text-surface-variant">Climate-controlled transport and anti-static protocols for critical infrastructure.</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Real Estate Staging -->
<div class="md:col-span-4 border-2 border-on-surface p-8 bg-surface-container-low flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 block-shadow-hover transition-all">
<div class="md:w-1/2">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" style="font-size: 40px;">home_work</span>
<h3 class="font-rr-headline-sm text-rr-headline-sm uppercase mt-2 mb-stack-md">Real Estate Staging</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Partnering with designers and agents to move furniture with surgical precision for high-end listing photography and open houses.</p>
</div>
<div class="md:w-1/2 h-48 w-full bg-cover bg-center border-2 border-on-surface" data-alt="A clean, minimalist high-end modern living room with neutral colors, large windows, and designer furniture, showcasing professional real estate staging in a bright light-mode aesthetic with sharp contrast and no-nonsense industrial precision." style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuA4lylxZx0TaJMMdyeJu1_AGNtGf3SW-QmJDt34RIEdkXVkyUGIvGlebPRjVuvr8ritb-fvzZ65r_mk3KumHmQd2qFeZ_FImW5izWt-XZHJEB0HNFdPpM6ccquMOjm3XC--FYkj_8yrl2xIOEZ1_3S9qnZqr2VDsjTdDTBR-qJ29KFFJyBHDX1g0gXWxMMI7ySKidpLY9jGfXkUvqcCtSe7wPKY2H0P765-vP9mDe65LfciKCQWCJSr5hk7q8JGDjQNWLyu4g2oq-cA')"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Industry Detail Cards -->
<section class="py-24 bg-surface-container">
<div class="max-w-rr-container-max mx-auto px-rr-margin-desktop">
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
<!-- Office Moving -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest border-2 border-on-surface overflow-hidden">
<div class="bg-primary-container h-8 w-full flex items-center px-4">
<span class="font-label-bold text-label-bold uppercase">Corporate Logistics</span>
</div>
<div class="p-10">
<h2 class="font-rr-headline-md text-rr-headline-md mb-stack-md">Office Moving - Minimized Downtime, Maximum Efficiency.</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-rr-stack-lg font-rr-body-md">Our weekend and overnight transition teams ensure your staff clocks out on Friday and clocks back in at the new location on Monday morning without missing a single beat. We handle cubicle teardown, server migration, and ergonomic furniture setup.</p>
<ul class="space-y-3">
<li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span> Asset Inventory Management</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span> IT &amp; Desktop Disconnect/Reconnect</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span> 24/7 Priority Support</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Retail -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest border-2 border-on-surface overflow-hidden">
<div class="bg-primary-container h-8 w-full flex items-center px-4">
<span class="font-label-bold text-label-bold uppercase">Inventory Handling</span>
</div>
<div class="p-10">
<h2 class="font-rr-headline-md text-rr-headline-md mb-stack-md">Retail - Secure Handling of High-Value Inventory.</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-rr-stack-lg font-rr-body-md">From delicate boutiques to large-scale warehouses, we provide itemized tracking for every piece of merchandise. Our secure, padded transport vehicles are designed specifically for luxury goods and sensitive retail equipment.</p>
<ul class="space-y-3">
<li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span> High-Security Transit</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span> White-Glove Unpacking</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span> Display Installation</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Case Study & Testimonial Section -->
<section class="py-24 bg-on-surface text-surface overflow-hidden">
<div class="max-w-rr-container-max mx-auto px-rr-margin-desktop">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
<div class="md:w-1/2">
<h2 class="font-rr-display-lg text-rr-display-lg-mobile md:text-rr-headline-md uppercase mb-rr-stack-lg border-l-8 border-primary-container pl-6">Case Study: Relocating a 50-Person Tech Startup in 24 Hours.</h2>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-surface-variant mb-rr-stack-lg">When 'Nexus-Labs' received immediate notice to vacate, RapidRelo deployed a 12-man specialized crew. We packed, transported, and reconfigured 50 workstations, two server racks, and a custom kitchen within a single 24-hour cycle.</p>
<div class="flex gap-8 border-t-2 border-outline-variant pt-8">
<div>
<div class="font-rr-display-lg text-primary-fixed text-rr-display-lg-mobile">24hr</div>
<div class="font-label-bold text-label-bold uppercase">Total Time</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="font-rr-display-lg text-primary-fixed text-rr-display-lg-mobile">Zero</div>
<div class="font-label-bold text-label-bold uppercase">Data Loss</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="md:w-1/2 bg-surface text-on-surface p-12 relative border-4 border-primary-container">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container absolute -top-8 left-8" style="font-size: 80px;">format_quote</span>
<blockquote class="relative z-10">
<p class="font-rr-headline-sm text-rr-headline-sm italic mb-rr-stack-lg leading-relaxed">
                                "The only movers we trust for our office expansions. RapidRelo treats our hardware like their own and their precision in timing is unmatched in the logistics industry."
                            </p>
<footer class="flex items-center gap-4">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary-container border-2 border-on-surface"></div>
<div>
<div class="font-label-bold text-label-bold uppercase">CEO of a local tech company</div>
<div class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Strategic Partner since 2021</div>
</div>
</footer>
</blockquote>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Final CTA -->
<section class="py-24 bg-primary-container border-y-4 border-on-surface">
<div class="max-w-rr-container-max mx-auto px-rr-margin-desktop text-center">
<h2 class="font-rr-display-lg text-rr-display-lg-mobile md:text-rr-display-lg uppercase mb-rr-stack-lg text-on-primary-fixed">Ready to Move Your Business?</h2>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-primary-fixed-variant mb-rr-stack-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">Our logistics experts are standing by to build a custom relocation plan for your organization.</p>
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
<button class="bg-on-surface text-surface font-label-bold text-label-bold uppercase px-12 py-5 border-2 border-on-surface block-shadow-hover block-shadow-active transition-all text-xl">
                        Get a Corporate Quote
                    </button>
<button class="bg-transparent text-on-surface font-label-bold text-label-bold uppercase px-12 py-5 border-2 border-on-surface block-shadow-hover block-shadow-active transition-all text-xl">
                        Speak to an Expert
                    </button>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>

</TemplateLayout>
